1
00:02:13,166 --> 00:02:15,041
[NARRATOR]
Last time on Dragon Ball Z,

2
00:02:15,125 --> 00:02:18,000
the fearsome duo of Babidi
and Majin Buu took off,

3
00:02:18,083 --> 00:02:20,500
seeking revenge for
Piccolo's failed attempt

4
00:02:20,583 --> 00:02:22,583
to end the dark wizard's life!

5
00:02:22,666 --> 00:02:24,125
Buu's penchant for annihilation

6
00:02:24,208 --> 00:02:26,000
caught even his
master off guard!

7
00:02:26,083 --> 00:02:28,125
Yet, the reckless destruction
left in their wake

8
00:02:28,208 --> 00:02:30,208
is merely a sample
of what the evil twosome

9
00:02:30,291 --> 00:02:32,416
has in store
for the Z Fighters,

10
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:34,916
whose defenses have
been severely thinned!

11
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,916
With Vegeta dead and
Gohan missing in action,

12
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,916
it seemed the world's
only hope for survival

13
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,375
would be Piccolo and Krillin--

14
00:02:41,458 --> 00:02:44,125
at least until Goten
and Trunks recover.

15
00:02:45,833 --> 00:02:48,916
[NARRATOR] But then Goku, after
being knocked out by Vegeta,

16
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:52,416
finally arose, along with the
Z Fighters' chances for victory.

17
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,791
Unaware of recent events,

18
00:02:53,875 --> 00:02:56,666
Goku attempted to intuit the
status of his teammates.

19
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:58,416
[GOKU]
I can still sense Buu,

20
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:01,291
but I can't sense Vegeta or
Gohan either! This isn't good!

21
00:03:01,375 --> 00:03:03,875
How long was I out
for? Too long...

22
00:03:05,083 --> 00:03:08,250
Something's happened,
something terrible!

23
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:10,958
It feels like Piccolo and
Krillin are back in action!

24
00:03:11,041 --> 00:03:12,916
They probably know
what's been going on.

25
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,916
Gohan... I'm sorry I
wasn't here for you.

26
00:03:17,666 --> 00:03:20,458
[NARRATOR] Goku returned to the
Lookout in search of answers,

27
00:03:20,541 --> 00:03:22,208
much to the surprise of
Piccolo and Krillin,

28
00:03:22,291 --> 00:03:24,250
who had all but
given up hope of ever

29
00:03:24,333 --> 00:03:25,750
seeing their friend again.

30
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:27,666
Reunited, they must
now find some way

31
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:30,500
to overpower the evil forces
of Babidi and Majin Buu!

32
00:03:30,583 --> 00:03:31,625
[GOKU]
Hi!

33
00:03:31,708 --> 00:03:33,708
He's real! He talks
and everything!

34
00:03:33,791 --> 00:03:37,250
[laughs]

35
00:03:47,416 --> 00:03:49,666
[PICCOLO] We're unaware of the
Supreme Kai's whereabouts,

36
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:52,125
though we faintly
detect he's alive.

37
00:03:52,208 --> 00:03:54,208
We'd just brought the little
ones back here to recuperate,

38
00:03:54,291 --> 00:03:55,875
when you showed up.

39
00:03:57,625 --> 00:04:02,041
[GOKU] Gohan, Supreme Kai,
even Vegeta, all gone...

40
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:06,125
What kind of monster
are we dealing with?!

41
00:04:06,208 --> 00:04:09,125
Majin Buu's power level
continues to increase at a rate

42
00:04:09,208 --> 00:04:12,750
unlike any enemy
we've encountered before.

43
00:04:12,833 --> 00:04:15,416
If we can't stop him from
destroying this world,

44
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:17,541
there will be nothing to
prevent him from wiping out

45
00:04:17,625 --> 00:04:20,333
every last trace of
life in the universe.

46
00:04:20,416 --> 00:04:22,166
Don't be such a downer, Piccolo,

47
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:24,750
of course we can stop Buu
now that Goku's alive.

48
00:04:24,833 --> 00:04:28,583
Sorry! The halo! What I meant to
say is that you may be "dead",

49
00:04:28,666 --> 00:04:30,125
but at least
you're not dead-dead,

50
00:04:30,208 --> 00:04:31,791
like Vegeta and Gohan.

51
00:04:31,875 --> 00:04:34,583
Oh! Stupid, Krillin,
think before you speak!

52
00:04:34,666 --> 00:04:37,958
Goku, you're the only one left
who can take on Majin Buu.

53
00:04:38,041 --> 00:04:40,125
So what are you waiting for?
Him to shove his pudgy,

54
00:04:40,208 --> 00:04:41,333
pink face up in yours?

55
00:04:41,416 --> 00:04:43,125
Come on, show that creep
a little of the ol'

56
00:04:43,208 --> 00:04:46,166
--Ka-me-ha-me-haaa!
--Krillin.

57
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:49,666
It's impossible, I just
can't beat him alone.

58
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,791
Huh?! But why not?

59
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:54,041
He's simply too
powerful an opponent.

60
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:56,000
E-Even for you? 

61
00:04:56,083 --> 00:04:57,833
Look, when Vegeta
and I were fighting,

62
00:04:57,916 --> 00:04:59,916
the two of us were
evenly matched.

63
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,791
He gave it everything he had,

64
00:05:01,875 --> 00:05:04,708
even his life, and he still
couldn't beat that thing.

65
00:05:06,541 --> 00:05:09,000
So what chance do
I have against him?

66
00:05:09,083 --> 00:05:11,041
[ALL gasp]

67
00:05:11,125 --> 00:05:16,000
If you can't, what hope
do we have? Goku...

68
00:05:16,083 --> 00:05:18,708
[GOKU] If only Vegeta
hadn't been so arrogant!

69
00:05:18,791 --> 00:05:20,708
Thinking he could
take on Buu alone...

70
00:05:20,791 --> 00:05:22,916
He'd still be alive and
we could work together!

71
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,083
No. Don't punish
yourself like this!

72
00:05:25,166 --> 00:05:27,208
It wouldn't have made
any difference.

73
00:05:27,291 --> 00:05:29,666
Not even an army of
Super Saiyans could have--

74
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,916
[GOKU]
I was going to say that if

75
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,666
Vegeta or Gohan
were still alive,

76
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:34,041
we could've done a fusion!

77
00:05:34,125 --> 00:05:37,916
Uh? Fuchsia? Like the
color of my shirt, sort of?

78
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,125
No, fusion.

79
00:05:39,208 --> 00:05:43,625
[gasps] Fusion?
You mean a merger?!

80
00:05:43,708 --> 00:05:45,541
Yeah, that's it, Dende!

81
00:05:45,625 --> 00:05:48,250
Oh, I've heard of such a
skill, back on Namek.

82
00:05:48,333 --> 00:05:50,750
A man from Metamor
once told me about it.

83
00:05:50,833 --> 00:05:53,500
Their people are quite
proficient at the technique.

84
00:05:53,583 --> 00:05:56,083
That's true! The Metamorese
I met in Other World

85
00:05:56,166 --> 00:05:58,333
are the ones that
showed me how to do it!

86
00:05:58,416 --> 00:06:00,041
So what is it, already?!

87
00:06:00,125 --> 00:06:02,708
It's an ancient merger art
that can be performed between

88
00:06:02,791 --> 00:06:06,125
two people of similar size
and physical ability.

89
00:06:06,208 --> 00:06:07,958
You wanna try that again?

90
00:06:08,041 --> 00:06:11,458
It's when two people combine
to form an entirely new being

91
00:06:11,541 --> 00:06:13,708
that's able to do things
neither could do alone.

92
00:06:13,791 --> 00:06:15,083
Like stopping an evil creature

93
00:06:15,166 --> 00:06:17,625
that's out to destroy the world
and everyone in it.

94
00:06:17,708 --> 00:06:18,541
[gasps]

95
00:06:18,625 --> 00:06:20,041
Now that I think about it,

96
00:06:20,125 --> 00:06:23,041
you and Nail were a sort of
fusion, too, weren't you?

97
00:06:23,125 --> 00:06:26,416
[PICCOLO]
Mm-hmm. Yes, we were, of a sort.

98
00:06:29,166 --> 00:06:31,416
[PICCOLo] Nail had been
badly wounded by Frieza

99
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:32,541
when I found him.

100
00:06:32,625 --> 00:06:34,958
He was dying.
And as his final act,

101
00:06:35,041 --> 00:06:37,333
he wished to impart
his powers to me.

102
00:06:37,416 --> 00:06:39,583
I was reluctant to
join with him at first,

103
00:06:39,666 --> 00:06:42,250
but his promise of
greater power proved...

104
00:06:42,333 --> 00:06:43,708
quite persuasive.

105
00:06:45,875 --> 00:06:48,083
[PICCOLO grunts]

106
00:06:48,166 --> 00:06:50,875
[PICCOLO] When it was over,
Nail's body had vanished,

107
00:06:50,958 --> 00:06:54,083
though I could still sense
his presence in me.

108
00:06:54,166 --> 00:06:56,125
I felt his strength
and his wisdom,

109
00:06:56,208 --> 00:06:58,125
so fresh and invigorating,

110
00:06:58,208 --> 00:07:02,333
yet familiar, as though it had
been at my fingertips all along.

111
00:07:02,416 --> 00:07:05,958
I stood up, reborn, knowing
that I was fully capable

112
00:07:06,041 --> 00:07:08,208
of avenging Nail
by taking on Frieza,

113
00:07:08,291 --> 00:07:11,208
or any other villain that
dared to cross my path.

114
00:07:11,291 --> 00:07:15,750
Wow. Unreal. My gosh.

115
00:07:15,833 --> 00:07:19,125
This is amazing!
I feel incredible!

116
00:07:19,208 --> 00:07:26,083
Yes! Yes! Yes! I can win! I
feel great! I can do this! Yes!

117
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:33,541
[PICCOLO] Yes! I'm home! I'm
alive! This is all a miracle!

118
00:07:33,625 --> 00:07:36,500
I'm awake! I'm wide awake!

119
00:07:38,541 --> 00:07:40,375
[PICCOLO laughs]

120
00:07:41,333 --> 00:07:43,125
[GOKU] The Namekian fusion
that you experienced, Piccolo,

121
00:07:43,208 --> 00:07:46,500
is actually quite different
from the Metamorese variety,

122
00:07:46,583 --> 00:07:49,333
Which is the process
I learned in Other World.

123
00:07:49,416 --> 00:07:50,916
The way I know is
only temporary,

124
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:54,625
and instead of one body playing
host, a new hybrid is formed,

125
00:07:54,708 --> 00:07:56,750
made up of characteristics
from both people.

126
00:07:56,833 --> 00:07:57,958
They transform into
a single warrior,

127
00:07:58,041 --> 00:08:00,208
capable of incredible
power and strength!

128
00:08:00,291 --> 00:08:01,958
Yes, that is different.

129
00:08:02,041 --> 00:08:04,000
But it seems the
end result is the same.

130
00:08:04,083 --> 00:08:05,208
I know when I fused with Nail,

131
00:08:05,291 --> 00:08:08,458
my power increased
exponentially.

132
00:08:08,541 --> 00:08:10,458
So if Gohan or Vegeta
were still alive,

133
00:08:10,541 --> 00:08:13,083
you could perform one of those
temporary fusions with them,

134
00:08:13,166 --> 00:08:14,416
couldn't you?

135
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,208
And then in your new form,

136
00:08:16,291 --> 00:08:18,791
you would have been able
to defeat Majin Buu.

137
00:08:18,875 --> 00:08:21,708
Nah, it probably wouldn't
have worked out so nicely

138
00:08:21,791 --> 00:08:23,916
even if Gohan or
Vegeta were alive.

139
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,500
It would take about a week to
show them what to do,

140
00:08:26,583 --> 00:08:28,708
but I'm only here on
Earth for this one day,

141
00:08:28,791 --> 00:08:30,666
not to mention that
even though I know how

142
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:32,000
these fusions work in theory,

143
00:08:32,083 --> 00:08:34,375
I've never taught
somebody else how to do it.

144
00:08:34,458 --> 00:08:35,958
And believe it or not,

145
00:08:36,041 --> 00:08:38,333
I've never actually been able to
try out a fusion in practice.

146
00:08:38,416 --> 00:08:42,208
No one in Other World is similar
enough to me to be compatible.

147
00:08:42,291 --> 00:08:43,250
[groans]

148
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:44,375
[DENDE sighs]

149
00:08:44,458 --> 00:08:45,791
[growls]

150
00:08:45,875 --> 00:08:48,625
So yeah, so much for that!
It was just a crazy idea!

151
00:08:48,708 --> 00:08:51,333
[KRILLIN]
Wait, Goku! No it's not!

152
00:08:51,416 --> 00:08:53,416
[GOKU] What are you
thinking about, Krillin?

153
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:56,125
You said you're about to go
back to the Other World, right?

154
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:57,958
And if Gohan and Vegeta
are really dead,

155
00:08:58,041 --> 00:08:59,958
then that's where they
must be too, correct?!

156
00:09:00,041 --> 00:09:03,125
So you can do a fusion with
them when you get back there!

157
00:09:03,208 --> 00:09:05,666
Oh, right!
Now that's a great idea!

158
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:08,666
Impossible. Once Goku
leaves this world

159
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,500
he won't be able to return.

160
00:09:10,583 --> 00:09:12,958
The fusion would
still do us no good.

161
00:09:13,041 --> 00:09:14,416
[BOTH sigh]

162
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:23,166
The young ones, sleeping.

163
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:25,583
Goten and Trunks
are almost exactly

164
00:09:25,666 --> 00:09:30,041
the same size, aren't they?
Could they do a fusion?

165
00:09:31,625 --> 00:09:33,416
Is that possible?

166
00:09:35,333 --> 00:09:36,625
Yeah!

167
00:09:36,708 --> 00:09:40,166
Thank you, Mr. Popo!
You know, that just might work!

168
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:40,791
[gasps]

169
00:09:40,875 --> 00:09:41,958
Really, Goku?!

170
00:09:42,041 --> 00:09:44,583
Mr. Popo, I love you!
You're a genius!

171
00:09:44,666 --> 00:09:47,333
Let's all give it up for
Mr. Popo, the genius!

172
00:09:47,416 --> 00:09:49,666
But Goku, do you think there's
enough time to teach them?

173
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,916
No. I'll work with them
as long as I can,

174
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,583
but they're gonna need
more time than I've got.

175
00:09:53,666 --> 00:09:56,500
Someone else will have
to pick up the slack.

176
00:09:56,583 --> 00:09:58,958
Piccolo, do you think
you'll be able to finish

177
00:09:59,041 --> 00:10:01,208
instructing the boys
after I've gone?

178
00:10:01,291 --> 00:10:02,500
I'll try.

179
00:10:02,583 --> 00:10:04,750
Woo-hoo-hoo!

180
00:10:04,833 --> 00:10:07,416
Goten and Trunks will
show Majin Buu who's boss!

181
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,458
He won't even know what hit him!

182
00:10:11,875 --> 00:10:13,291
[PICCOLO]
Not so fast, Krillin.

183
00:10:13,375 --> 00:10:14,458
Huh?

184
00:10:14,541 --> 00:10:16,125
According to Goku,
it will take some time

185
00:10:16,208 --> 00:10:18,500
before they've mastered
the art of fusion

186
00:10:18,583 --> 00:10:20,375
and are ready to
make their attack.

187
00:10:20,458 --> 00:10:22,083
Meanwhile,
many innocent people

188
00:10:22,166 --> 00:10:25,583
will be lost in the wake of
Majin Buu's destruction.

189
00:10:25,666 --> 00:10:27,916
I'm talking about
total annihilation.

190
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:31,250
Everything and everyone
on this planet, wiped out.

191
00:10:33,416 --> 00:10:34,875
It's a gamble.

192
00:10:34,958 --> 00:10:37,541
So we must prepare ourselves for
anything that comes our way

193
00:10:37,625 --> 00:10:40,541
until the boys have mastered
fusion and are ready to go.

194
00:10:42,083 --> 00:10:43,458
You're right,

195
00:10:43,541 --> 00:10:45,125
but I'm confident these two
can learn how to do this.

196
00:10:45,208 --> 00:10:46,875
And we can always use
the Dragon Balls

197
00:10:46,958 --> 00:10:48,833
to clean up the
damage at the end.

198
00:10:48,916 --> 00:10:50,458
[KRILLIN] You think we
still have a chance?

199
00:10:50,541 --> 00:10:53,416
We can't ever give up
hope, you guys.

200
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,625
And right now,

201
00:10:54,708 --> 00:10:56,875
Trunks and Goten are
the world's best hope.

202
00:10:56,958 --> 00:10:59,583
We should know by now not to
underestimate the young--

203
00:10:59,666 --> 00:11:03,291
especially when they're
a couple of Super Saiyans.

204
00:11:03,375 --> 00:11:06,833
[BABIDI] Ah, Buu! So many places
to blow, people to scream!

205
00:11:06,916 --> 00:11:09,708
[BUU giggles]

206
00:11:09,791 --> 00:11:11,750
[BABIDI]
Buu?

207
00:11:11,833 --> 00:11:13,083
[thinking]
He's a smooth flyer,

208
00:11:13,166 --> 00:11:15,250
but as a conversationalist,
he's sort of a bum.

209
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:17,166
[BABIDI]
Hel-lo.

210
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:19,250
Buu?

211
00:11:19,333 --> 00:11:22,083
[BABIDI] Ah yes, this location
is full of potential!

212
00:11:22,166 --> 00:11:25,041
Or should I say,
"was" full of potential.

213
00:11:25,125 --> 00:11:26,750
[BABIDI giggles]

214
00:11:26,833 --> 00:11:28,083
[RIDERS scream]

215
00:11:28,166 --> 00:11:31,000
[BUU squeals]

216
00:11:31,083 --> 00:11:33,208
[BABIDI] Wait! Buu!
What are you doing?!

217
00:11:33,291 --> 00:11:34,791
We're not here
for your amusement!

218
00:11:34,875 --> 00:11:35,958
We're here for mine! Stop!

219
00:11:36,041 --> 00:11:42,916
I'm not wearing
a safety belt! [screams]

220
00:11:46,625 --> 00:11:48,500
[BABIDI]
No, no, not the loop!

221
00:11:48,583 --> 00:11:51,000
[BABIDI screams]

222
00:11:51,083 --> 00:11:53,166
[BABIDI] Stop, Buu!
I don't like this ri--!

223
00:11:53,250 --> 00:12:01,750
[screams]

224
00:12:02,958 --> 00:12:06,000
[BABIDI]
I command you to stop!

225
00:12:06,083 --> 00:12:07,583
If you don't save me fast,

226
00:12:07,666 --> 00:12:09,583
I'll put you in your shell until
the next ice age passes over!

227
00:12:09,666 --> 00:12:12,500
I can't fall! Geniuses like
me are highly breakable!

228
00:12:16,708 --> 00:12:17,625
Cool puppets.

229
00:12:17,708 --> 00:12:19,125
They're way life-like!

230
00:12:21,833 --> 00:12:24,416
Your playtime... is over!

231
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,000
[BUU grunts]

232
00:12:25,083 --> 00:12:25,958
[RIDERS scream]

233
00:12:26,041 --> 00:12:27,416
[BUU]
Buu!

234
00:12:50,458 --> 00:12:53,791
Bulma, why don't you just get it
over with and summon the dragon?

235
00:12:57,416 --> 00:12:59,000
Does he just pop
up out of them?

236
00:12:59,083 --> 00:13:00,916
She may have a
pretty enough face,

237
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,708
but her skull sure is thick!

238
00:13:02,791 --> 00:13:04,125
Mind your
manners, Oolong.

239
00:13:04,208 --> 00:13:05,708
Not everyone is as
worldly as you.

240
00:13:05,791 --> 00:13:08,708
Videl, just keep your
eyes on the balls.

241
00:13:08,791 --> 00:13:10,500
I'm not so naive, you know.

242
00:13:10,583 --> 00:13:13,500
I've just never seen
a magical dragon before.

243
00:13:13,583 --> 00:13:16,041
Okay, now do you remember
the spell to release him?

244
00:13:16,125 --> 00:13:17,166
You know all the words?

245
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:18,541
Of course,

246
00:13:18,625 --> 00:13:21,416
I'm not gonna pull a Frieza
and screw it up, Yamcha!

247
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,875
Bulma, I think Frieza failed

248
00:13:22,958 --> 00:13:25,166
because he wore
too many clothes!

249
00:13:25,250 --> 00:13:27,458
--[PUAR sqeauls]
--[OOLONG yells]

250
00:13:27,541 --> 00:13:29,458
Hey, now!
Put it to rest will ya?!

251
00:13:29,541 --> 00:13:32,708
Now's not the time for your
shenanigans! Chauvinist pig.

252
00:13:32,791 --> 00:13:34,416
So, there's a spell
involved, huh?

253
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:37,333
Oh, I guess that
would make sense.

254
00:13:37,416 --> 00:13:39,125
Bulma, go ahead, dear.

255
00:13:39,208 --> 00:13:41,916
Call the dragon so we
can wish all those poor people

256
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,916
who your Vegeta destroyed at the
Tournament today back to life.

257
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,000
That is the plan.

258
00:13:53,041 --> 00:13:59,041
