I summon you forth! Shenron!

259
00:14:19,208 --> 00:14:21,208
[gasps]

260
00:14:25,416 --> 00:14:27,583
[KRILLIN] All right,
I'm gonna go get everybody

261
00:14:27,666 --> 00:14:28,958
and bring 'em back here.

262
00:14:29,041 --> 00:14:30,250
[PICCOLO]
Good.

263
00:14:30,333 --> 00:14:31,708
[GOKU]
Take care, Krillin!

264
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:34,916
[ALL]
Huh?

265
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,541
[KRILLIN] Is it Daylight
Savings Time already

266
00:14:36,625 --> 00:14:37,666
and someone forgot to tell me?!

267
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:40,958
Oh no, why has it
suddenly gone dark?!

268
00:14:41,041 --> 00:14:42,416
Not good.

269
00:14:48,083 --> 00:14:50,958
Someone's released
Shenron! Who and why?

270
00:14:51,041 --> 00:14:52,333
My money's on Bulma.

271
00:14:52,416 --> 00:14:54,291
Who else could gather those
Dragon Balls so fast?

272
00:14:54,375 --> 00:14:56,125
But she can't know about
everything that's happened.

273
00:14:56,208 --> 00:14:59,125
So why call the Dragon now?

274
00:14:59,208 --> 00:15:02,000
[gasps] She knows
Vegeta slaughtered a lot

275
00:15:02,083 --> 00:15:04,416
of innocent people at the
martial arts stadium today!

276
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:07,041
Bulma must be trying to
bring them all back to life!

277
00:15:07,125 --> 00:15:10,041
Oh no! That'll ruin everything!

278
00:15:10,125 --> 00:15:11,625
Once two wishes are fulfilled,

279
00:15:11,708 --> 00:15:13,708
we'll have to wait a whole year
before we can make another one!

280
00:15:13,791 --> 00:15:15,833
[gasping]

281
00:15:15,916 --> 00:15:19,166
[GOKU] All right, then. I'll
just have to go and stop her.

282
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:26,583
[GOKU using telepathy]
Bulma? Bulma?!

283
00:15:26,666 --> 00:15:28,250
Bulma, where are you?

284
00:15:33,791 --> 00:15:37,958
Darn! Bulma's life-force
is difficult for me to trace.

285
00:15:38,041 --> 00:15:41,250
Everything feels just so
clouded right now on Earth.

286
00:15:48,166 --> 00:15:53,416
[SHENRON growls]

287
