going to have to faint now.

293
00:16:30,458 --> 00:16:33,041
[SHENRON]
You try my patience! Speak!

294
00:16:33,125 --> 00:16:36,333
[BULMA] Hmm, now how exactly
should I phrase this wish?

295
00:16:36,416 --> 00:16:37,916
[YAMCHA] I thought you had
this figured out!

296
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,833
