299
00:16:45,083 --> 00:16:46,375
That'll do.

300
00:16:46,458 --> 00:16:48,625
Oh man, can people
actually be brought back

301
00:16:48,708 --> 00:16:50,375
from the dead like that?

302
00:16:50,458 --> 00:16:56,541
