309
00:17:40,166 --> 00:17:41,750
Goku?!

310
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,833
Goku, where on
Earth have you been?

311
00:17:43,916 --> 00:17:45,333
[gasps, growls

312
00:17:45,416 --> 00:17:47,458
And where is Gohan?
And Goten?!

313
00:17:47,541 --> 00:17:49,500
ChiChi, there's
no time to explain.

314
00:17:49,583 --> 00:17:53,000
Please trust me.
Dende, can you hear me?

315
00:17:53,083 --> 00:17:53,666
[DENDE using telepathy]
Yes!

316
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,000
I arrived too late.

317
00:17:55,083 --> 00:17:57,416
The dragon has already
fulfilled their first wish

318
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:59,500
and now he wants to know
what their second one is.

319
00:17:59,583 --> 00:18:01,041
What should I do?

320
00:18:01,125 --> 00:18:02,666
Then there is still hope.

321
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:04,041
Tell Shenron
that you want to save

322
00:18:04,125 --> 00:18:05,666
the other wish for another time.

323
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:07,125
If only one has been granted,

324
00:18:07,208 --> 00:18:08,250
then we can
use that wish again

325
00:18:08,333 --> 00:18:10,083
when only four
months have passed.

326
00:18:10,166 --> 00:18:12,791
[GOKU using telepathy] All
right, I'll take care of that.

327
00:18:12,875 --> 00:18:15,666
Oh, and you guys. I can't
believe I almost forgot.

328
00:18:15,750 --> 00:18:17,333
I'm bringing you
all back with me,

329
00:18:17,416 --> 00:18:20,083
once I'm finished with my
business here. So get ready.

330
00:18:20,166 --> 00:18:21,833
[DENDE using telepathy] We'll
prepare for your return, Goku.

331
00:18:21,916 --> 00:18:23,833
Thanks. Shenron!

332
00:18:23,916 --> 00:18:27,166
You don't have to grant any more
wishes today. Thank you!

333
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:29,166
We'll call you again sometime!

334
00:18:29,250 --> 00:18:33,000
As you wish. Farewell.

335
00:18:48,458 --> 00:18:50,250
You wanna tell me what's
gotten into you Goku?

336
00:18:50,333 --> 00:18:51,833
We still had a
perfectly good wish

337
00:18:51,916 --> 00:18:53,625
we could have used to help!

338
00:18:55,916 --> 00:18:57,291
[KIBITO thinking]
I don't understand.

339
00:18:57,375 --> 00:19:01,083
My body appears to be in
perfect physical condition.

340
00:19:01,166 --> 00:19:03,791
And this place,
something's wrong.

341
00:19:03,875 --> 00:19:06,541
I shouldn't be here! Wait...

342
00:19:06,625 --> 00:19:10,833
I remember now.
I was attacked by Dabura.

343
00:19:16,375 --> 00:19:18,666
Now, let's begin.

344
00:19:26,916 --> 00:19:28,333
[gasps]

345
00:19:34,333 --> 00:19:36,375
Haaa...!

346
00:19:36,458 --> 00:19:39,000
[KIBITO screams]

347
00:19:43,208 --> 00:19:47,000
Have I been brought
back to life? A miracle!

348
00:19:47,083 --> 00:19:48,458
[gasps]

349
00:19:51,208 --> 00:19:53,833
[KIBITO] The Supreme Kai!
I must find and protect him!

350
00:19:53,916 --> 00:19:55,583
