the last hope of the universe.

361
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:51,000
[GOKU]
So, there you go.

362
00:20:51,083 --> 00:20:53,083
Now, if you'll all come back
with me to the Lookout,

363
00:20:53,166 --> 00:20:55,791
