shouldn't be any problem!

367
00:21:01,208 --> 00:21:02,583
That's the spirit!

368
00:21:03,916 --> 00:21:05,041
Now, everyone.

369
00:21:05,125 --> 00:21:06,416
As long as you're
connected to me,

370
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:08,416
we can all travel by
"Instant Transmission!"

371
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:09,791
[VIDEL thinking]
This is like some wonderful

372
00:21:09,875 --> 00:21:11,250
fantasy land where,
just when I think

373
00:21:11,333 --> 00:21:14,916
it can't possibly get
any weirder, it does!

